@startuml
!theme materia-outline

title REQ_IVI_012: UDS 0x14 - Clear DTC (ASIL-B)

actor "Diagnostic Tester\n(CANoe)" as Tester
participant "CAN Bus" as CAN
box "vECU (Target)" #f9f9f9
    participant "DCM\n(Diagnostic Communication Manager)" as DCM
    participant "DEM\n(Diagnostic Event Manager)" as DEM
    participant "NvM\n(Non-volatile Memory)" as NVM
end box

== Extended Diagnostic Session ==

Tester -> CAN : 0x10 03\n(Extended Diagnostic Session)
activate CAN
CAN -> DCM : Session Request
activate DCM
DCM -> DCM : Validate Session Request
DCM --> CAN : 0x50 03\n(Positive Response)
CAN --> Tester : Session Active
deactivate DCM
deactivate CAN

note right of DCM
    **Session Established**
    • Extended Diagnostic Mode
    • Security Access Required
end note

== Clear DTC Request ==

Tester -> CAN : 0x14 FF FF FF\n(Clear All DTCs)
activate CAN
note right: REQ_IVI_012\nSuccess Rate: >99%

CAN -> DCM : Clear DTC Service
activate DCM

DCM -> DEM : Request Clear All DTCs
activate DEM

DEM -> DEM : Validate Request\n(Check Session State)

alt Clear DTC Successful
    DEM -> NVM : Erase DTC Storage
    activate NVM
    NVM -> NVM : Clear Flash Memory\n(DTC Area: 0x8000-0x8FFF)
    NVM --> DEM : Erase Complete
    deactivate NVM

    DEM -> DEM : Reset DTC Counters\nReset Freeze Frames
    DEM --> DCM : Clear Successful
    deactivate DEM

    DCM --> CAN : 0x54\n(Positive Response)
    CAN --> Tester : DTCs Cleared
    deactivate DCM
    deactivate CAN

else Clear DTC Failed
    DEM --> DCM : Clear Failed\n(Memory Error)
    deactivate DEM

    DCM --> CAN : 0x7F 14 22\n(Conditions Not Correct)
    CAN --> Tester : Clear Failed
    deactivate DCM
    deactivate CAN
end

== Verification ==

Tester -> CAN : 0x19 02 FF\n(Read DTC by Status Mask)
CAN -> DCM : Read DTC Request
activate DCM
DCM -> DEM : Get Stored DTCs
activate DEM
DEM --> DCM : No DTCs Found
deactivate DEM
DCM --> CAN : 0x59 02\n(No DTC Available)
CAN --> Tester : Verification Complete
deactivate DCM

note over Tester
    **REQ_IVI_012 Verified**
    • All DTCs cleared
    • Re-query returns empty
    • Success rate: >99%
end note

@enduml
@startuml
!theme materia-outline

title REQ_IVI_013, 047: UDS 0x34 - OTA Download (ASIL-B)

actor "OTA Server\n(CANoe)" as Server
participant "CAN Bus" as CAN
box "vECU (Target)" #f9f9f9
    participant "DCM" as DCM
    participant "OTA_Update_Agent" as OTA
    participant "Flash Memory" as FLASH
    participant "DEM" as DEM
end box

== Programming Session ==

Server -> CAN : 0x10 02\n(Programming Session)
activate CAN
CAN -> DCM : Session Request
activate DCM
DCM --> CAN : 0x50 02\n(Positive Response)
CAN --> Server : Programming Mode Active
deactivate DCM
deactivate CAN

== Security Access ==

Server -> CAN : 0x27 01\n(Request Seed)
CAN -> DCM : Security Access Request
activate DCM
DCM -> DCM : Generate Seed\n(Random: 0x12345678)
DCM --> CAN : 0x67 01 12 34 56 78\n(Seed Response)
CAN --> Server : Seed Received
deactivate DCM

Server -> Server : Calculate Key\n(Algorithm: AES-128)

Server -> CAN : 0x27 02 AB CD EF 01\n(Send Key)
CAN -> DCM : Security Key
activate DCM
DCM -> DCM : Validate Key
DCM --> CAN : 0x67 02\n(Key Accepted)
CAN --> Server : Security Unlocked
deactivate DCM

== Request Download (0x34) ==

Server -> CAN : 0x34 00 44\n00 08 00 00\n00 00 10 00\n(Address: 0x80000, Size: 4096 bytes)
activate CAN
note right: REQ_IVI_013\nSuccess Rate: >98%

CAN -> DCM : Request Download
activate DCM

DCM -> OTA : Verify Memory & Security
activate OTA

OTA -> OTA : Check Address Range\nCheck Available Space

alt Memory Available
    OTA -> FLASH : Allocate Flash Space\n(Address: 0x80000-0x81000)
    activate FLASH
    FLASH --> OTA : Space Allocated
    deactivate FLASH

    OTA --> DCM : Download Accepted\n(Max Block Size: 256 bytes)
    deactivate OTA

    DCM --> CAN : 0x74 20 10\n(Max Block: 0x1000 = 4096 bytes)
    CAN --> Server : Ready for Transfer
    deactivate DCM
    deactivate CAN

else Memory Full
    OTA --> DCM : Insufficient Memory
    deactivate OTA
    DCM --> CAN : 0x7F 34 70\n(Upload/Download Not Accepted)
    CAN --> Server : Download Rejected
    deactivate DCM
    deactivate CAN
end

== Data Transfer (0x36) ==

loop Transfer Blocks (16 blocks × 256 bytes)
    Server -> CAN : 0x36 01 [256 bytes data]\n(Block Sequence: 0x01)
    CAN -> DCM : Transfer Data
    activate DCM
    DCM -> FLASH : Write Payload to Flash
    activate FLASH
    FLASH --> DCM : Write Complete
    deactivate FLASH
    DCM --> CAN : 0x76 01\n(Block Received)
    CAN --> Server : Block ACK
    deactivate DCM
end

note over Server
    **REQ_IVI_047**
    • Parameter OTA: <45s
    • Success Rate: >99%
    • Lighting Theme Update
end note

== Transfer Exit (0x37) ==

Server -> CAN : 0x37\n(Request Transfer Exit)
CAN -> DCM : Transfer Exit Request
activate DCM
DCM -> OTA : Finalize Transfer
activate OTA
OTA -> OTA : Calculate Checksum\n(CRC32: 0xABCDEF01)
OTA --> DCM : Transfer Complete
deactivate OTA
DCM --> CAN : 0x77\n(Transfer Exit OK)
CAN --> Server : Download Complete
deactivate DCM

== Integrity Check (0x31) ==

Server -> CAN : 0x31 01 02 02\n(Check Programming Dependencies)
CAN -> DCM : Routine Control Request
activate DCM
DCM -> OTA : Verify Integrity
activate OTA

OTA -> OTA : Checksum Validation\nSignature Verification

alt Validation Successful
    OTA --> DCM : Integrity OK
    deactivate OTA
    DCM --> CAN : 0x71 01 02 02\n(Routine Complete)
    CAN --> Server : Validation Passed
    deactivate DCM

else Validation Failed
    OTA --> DCM : Integrity Check Failed
    deactivate OTA
    DCM -> DEM : Log DTC (0xC00400)
    activate DEM
    DEM --> DCM : DTC Logged
    deactivate DEM
    DCM --> CAN : 0x7F 31 72\n(General Programming Failure)
    CAN --> Server : Validation Failed
    deactivate DCM
end

note over OTA
    **REQ_IVI_013 Complete**
    • Download Success: >98%
    • Integrity Verified
    • Ready for Activation
end note

@enduml
