!theme silver

title REQ_IVI_015: OTA Failure Auto-Recovery (ASIL-C)

participant "OTA Server" as Server
participant "CAN Bus" as CAN
box "vECU (Target)" #f9f9f9
    participant "OTA_Update_Agent" as OTA
    participant "Flash Memory" as FLASH
    participant "Bootloader" as BL
    participant "DEM" as DEM
end box

== OTA Update in Progress ==

Server -> CAN : 0x36 0A [256 bytes]\n(Block 10/16)
CAN -> OTA : Transfer Data Block 10
activate OTA
OTA -> FLASH : Write to Flash
activate FLASH

== Power Failure Occurs ==

note over FLASH #Red
    **POWER CUT**
    Simulated by CANoe
    Fault Injection
end note

FLASH --> OTA : Write Interrupted
deactivate FLASH
OTA -> OTA : Detect Incomplete Transfer
deactivate OTA

== System Reboot ==

note over BL: **Bootloader Startup**\nPower Restored

BL -> BL : Check Application Integrity
BL -> FLASH : Read Application CRC
activate FLASH
FLASH --> BL : CRC Mismatch\n(Corrupted Application)
deactivate FLASH

BL -> BL : **Recovery Decision**\nApplication Invalid

== Automatic Rollback ==

BL -> FLASH : Load Backup Image\n(Previous Valid Version)
activate FLASH
note right: REQ_IVI_015\nRecovery: 100%

FLASH -> FLASH : Copy Backup to Active\n(Address: 0x90000 → 0x80000)
FLASH --> BL : Rollback Complete
deactivate FLASH

BL -> BL : Verify Backup Integrity
BL -> FLASH : Read Backup CRC
activate FLASH
FLASH --> BL : CRC Valid
deactivate FLASH

== Application Restart ==

BL -> OTA : Start Application\n(Previous Version)
activate OTA

OTA -> OTA : Initialize System
OTA -> DEM : Log Recovery Event\n(DTC: 0xC00500)
activate DEM
DEM --> OTA : Event Logged
deactivate DEM

OTA --> CAN : System Ready\n(Fallback Version Active)
CAN --> Server : Recovery Complete

note over OTA
    **REQ_IVI_015 Verified**
    • Auto Rollback: 100%
    • Previous Version Restored
    • System Functional
    • DTC Logged for Analysis
end note

deactivate OTA

@enduml
@startuml
!theme silver

title REQ_IVI_014: Post-OTA Function Verification (ASIL-B)

participant "Test System\n(CANoe)" as Test
participant "CAN Bus" as CAN
box "vECU (Updated)" #f9f9f9
    participant "OTA_Update_Agent" as OTA
    participant "Lighting_Controller" as LIGHT
    participant "Safety_Manager" as SAFETY
    participant "Diagnostic_Stack" as DIAG
end box

== OTA Update Complete ==

note over OTA: New Software Version: v2.1.0\nPrevious Version: v2.0.5

== Automated Function Test ==

Test -> CAN : Start Function Verification\n(UDS 0x31 01 FF 01)
CAN -> OTA : Verification Request
activate OTA

OTA -> OTA : Initialize Test Sequence
note right: REQ_IVI_014\nSuccess Rate: >99%

== Test 1: Lighting Function ==

OTA -> LIGHT : Test Sport Mode Lighting
activate LIGHT
LIGHT -> LIGHT : Simulate Speed 60 km/h\nExpected: BLUE
LIGHT --> OTA : Color: BLUE ✅
deactivate LIGHT

== Test 2: Safety Function ==

OTA -> SAFETY : Test Reverse Safety Alert
activate SAFETY
SAFETY -> SAFETY : Simulate Gear R\nExpected: UI + Light ON
SAFETY --> OTA : Alert Active ✅
deactivate SAFETY

== Test 3: Diagnostic Function ==

OTA -> DIAG : Test DTC Storage
activate DIAG
DIAG -> DIAG : Inject Test Fault\nExpected: DTC 0xC00001
DIAG --> OTA : DTC Stored ✅
deactivate DIAG

== Test Results ==

OTA -> OTA : Aggregate Test Results\n• Lighting: PASS\n• Safety: PASS\n• Diagnostic: PASS

alt All Tests Passed
    OTA --> CAN : 0x71 01 FF 01\n(Verification Successful)
    CAN --> Test : All Functions OK
    deactivate OTA

else Any Test Failed
    OTA --> CAN : 0x7F 31 72\n(Verification Failed)
    CAN --> Test : Function Test Failed
    deactivate OTA

    note over Test #Red
        **Rollback Triggered**
        Automatic return to
        previous version
    end note
end

note over OTA
    **REQ_IVI_014 Complete**
    • Automated Test: >99% success
    • All Functions Verified
    • System Ready for Operation
end note

@enduml
